+| `ZEND_BIND_HOST` | `127.0.0.1` | Daemon bind address (use LAN IP for remote) |
+| `ZEND_BIND_PORT` | `8080` | Daemon port |
+| `ZEND_DAEMON_URL` | `http://127.0.0.1:8080` | CLI daemon URL |
